description:
Task bar. App grid, favorites, workspaces and tasks in panel.

 Drag and drop favorite, task, dash item or app grid item to any workspace (you cannot reorder tasks inside a workspace). Change Places label to an icon.

  Edit the string array 'org.gnome.desktop.wm.preferences.workspace-names' gsettings key (through dconf editor, e.g.).

 Changelog: https://github.com/BriRE/babar/issues/2
name: BaBar Task Bar
